# Extract more pages for method details
with open('./11-moverscore/moverscore/paper.pdf', 'rb') as f:
    reader = PyPDF2.PdfReader(f)
    num_pages = len(reader.pages)
    text = ''
    for i in range(10, min(num_pages, 20)):
        text += reader.pages[i].extract_text() + '\n'

print(text[:3000])
